title: NPC_Test_Node
---
<<set_left Ren>>
<<enter_left>>
Ren: Let's test if the backend is working.
Ren: Should I make the good choice, or the bad choice?

-> Make the Good Choice
    <<record_choice "world_hospital" 1>>
    Ren: I made the right call. The score should be 1.
-> Make the Bad Choice
    <<record_choice "world_hospital" 0>>
    Ren: I messed up. The score should be 0.

Ren: Let's check the Unity Console!
<<exit_left>>
